    <subfield code="m">Here we have used the relations cos th = 1- 1 2 th2 +O(th4 ) and sin th = th+O(th3 ) for th [?] 0 and cos th = -1+ 1 2 (p-th)2 +O((p-th)4 ) and sin th = p - th + O((p - th)3 ) for th [?] p</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="999" ind1="C" ind2="5">
